    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You open your mind to the metaphysical, enabling you to sense nearby spirits. Even if you aren’t @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.TiNDYUGlMmxzxBYU]{Searching}, you get a check to find haunts and spirits in the area. You gain a +1 status bonus to the following checks regarding haunts or spirits: Perception checks to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.BlAOM2X92SI6HMtJ]{Seek}, attempts to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.B2BpIZFHoF9Kjzpx]{Recall Knowledge}, skill checks to determine the reason for their existence, and skill checks to disable a haunt. You also gain a +1 status bonus to AC and saving throws against haunts and spirits.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Heightened (6th)</strong> The spell’s duration lasts until the next time you make your daily preparations.</p>",
